channel.title: CVE Feed for SAP_SE -- SAP HANA Client
channel.description: The latest CVEs for SAP_SE -- SAP HANA Client

item.title: CVE-2024-45277|2024-10-08T09:52:33.850Z -- sap_se -- sap%20hana%20client
item.description: The SAP HANA Node.js client package versions from 2.0.0 before 2.21.31 is impacted by Prototype Pollution vulnerability allowing an attacker to add arbitrary properties to global object prototypes. This is due to improper user input sanitation when using the nestTables feature causing low impact on the availability of the application. This has no impact on Confidentiality and Integrity.
